  Dedicated FAQ page with hero, expanded smart-faq section, and CTA.
  Assign this template to a Shopify page at: Pages → FAQ → Template suffix → faq
{% endcomment %}

<div class="faq-page">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="faq-hero">
    <div class="faq-page-container">
      <h1>{{ page.title | default: 'Frequently Asked Questions' }}</h1>
      <p>Everything you need to know about our cleaning and landscaping services. Can't find your answer? <a href="/pages/contact-us">Contact us</a> — we're happy to help.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Smart FAQ Section (reusable section with schema markup) -->
  <section class="faq-main">
    <div class="faq-page-container">
      {% section 'smart-faq' %}
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Additional Categories -->
  <section class="faq-categories">
    <div class="faq-page-container">
      <h2>More Questions by Topic</h2>

      <div class="faq-cat-grid">
        <!-- Cleaning Services -->
        <div class="faq-cat-card">
          <h3>Cleaning Services</h3>
          <div class="faq-cat-list">
            <details>
              <summary>What's included in a recurring cleaning?</summary>
              <p>Our recurring cleaning covers all main living areas: vacuuming, mopping, dusting, kitchen counters and appliances (exterior), bathroom sanitizing, trash removal, and general tidying. We follow a detailed checklist every visit so nothing gets missed.</p>
            </details>
            <details>
              <summary>What's the difference between a deep clean and a recurring clean?</summary>
              <p>A deep clean is a thorough top-to-bottom scrub — inside cabinets, behind appliances, baseboards, light fixtures, window sills, and more. We recommend a deep clean as your first visit, then switch to recurring maintenance cleanings to keep everything fresh.</p>
            </details>
            <details>
              <summary>Do I need to be home during the cleaning?</summary>
              <p>Nope! Many of our clients give us a key, a lockbox code, or a garage code. We'll lock up when we leave and you'll come home to a spotless house. We're fully insured so your home is always protected.</p>
            </details>
            <details>
              <summary>What if I need to reschedule?</summary>
              <p>Life happens — just give us 24 hours' notice and we'll happily reschedule at no charge. Same-day cancellations may be subject to a fee since we've reserved the time for your home.</p>
            </details>
            <details>
              <summary>Do you bring your own supplies and equipment?</summary>
              <p>Yes, we bring everything — vacuums, mops, cleaning solutions, and all supplies. We use eco-friendly products by default, but if you have a preferred product you'd like us to use, just let us know.</p>
            </details>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Landscaping -->
        <div class="faq-cat-card">
          <h3>Landscaping & Lawn Care</h3>
          <div class="faq-cat-list">
            <details>
              <summary>How often should I have my lawn mowed?</summary>
              <p>During growing season (April through October), we recommend weekly or bi-weekly mowing. We'll adjust the schedule based on your lawn's growth rate, grass type, and the season. Winter mowing is rarely needed in our area.</p>
            </details>
            <details>
              <summary>Do you handle leaf removal and seasonal cleanup?</summary>
              <p>Absolutely. Our seasonal cleanup includes leaf blowing and removal, bed cleanup, debris clearing, gutter clearing, and prepping your yard for the next season. Most clients book spring and fall cleanups.</p>
            </details>
            <details>
              <summary>Can you help with landscaping design and planting?</summary>
              <p>Yes! We offer landscape design consultations, mulching, bed edging, shrub and tree planting, flower bed installation, and hardscape work. We'll work with you to create a plan that fits your style and budget.</p>
            </details>
            <details>
              <summary>What's included in your lawn maintenance package?</summary>
              <p>Our lawn maintenance includes mowing, edging, trimming, and blowing all walkways and driveways clean. Add-ons like fertilization, aeration, and weed control are available at an additional cost.</p>
            </details>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Pricing & Booking -->
        <div class="faq-cat-card">
          <h3>Pricing & Booking</h3>
          <div class="faq-cat-list">
            <details>
              <summary>How is pricing determined?</summary>
              <p>Pricing depends on your home size, number of bedrooms and bathrooms, service frequency, and any add-ons you select. Our online quote calculator gives you an instant estimate, or we can provide a custom quote after learning about your specific needs.</p>
            </details>
            <details>
              <summary>Do you offer bundle discounts?</summary>
              <p>Yes — bundle cleaning and landscaping services together and save 10%. It's the easiest way to keep your whole property looking great with one company and one bill.</p>
            </details>
            <details>
              <summary>What payment methods do you accept?</summary>
              <p>We accept credit/debit cards, Venmo, Zelle, and checks. For recurring clients, we can set up automatic billing so you never have to think about it.</p>
            </details>
            <details>
              <summary>Is there a minimum service charge?</summary>
              <p>Our minimum for cleaning services starts at $100, and lawn mowing starts at $40. Exact pricing depends on your property size and the services requested.</p>
            </details>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Trust & Safety -->
        <div class="faq-cat-card">
          <h3>Trust & Safety</h3>
          <div class="faq-cat-list">
            <details>
              <summary>Are your employees background checked?</summary>
              <p>Yes. Every team member goes through a thorough background check and vetting process before they ever enter a client's home. Your safety and trust are our top priorities.</p>
            </details>
            <details>
              <summary>What happens if something is damaged during service?</summary>
              <p>We're fully insured. If something is accidentally damaged during a visit, report it within 24 hours and we'll handle the claim quickly. We treat your home like our own — damage is extremely rare.</p>
            </details>
            <details>
              <summary>Do you serve commercial properties?</summary>
              <p>Yes! We handle offices, rental properties, Airbnb turnovers, and commercial spaces. Contact us for a custom commercial quote — pricing varies based on square footage and frequency.</p>
            </details>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="faq-cta">
    <div class="faq-page-container">
      <h2>Still Have Questions?</h2>
      <p>We're real people, not a call center. Reach out anytime.</p>
      <div class="faq-cta-buttons">
        <a href="/pages/request-a-quote" class="faq-cta-primary">Get a Free Estimate</a>
        <a href="tel:4343510335" class="faq-cta-secondary">Call 434-351-0335</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

